# Hex Grid

A Django implementation of a hexagonal grid system.

Inspired by https://www.redblobgames.com/grids/hexagons/.

This app implements flat-top hexes using the cube (q,r,s) system.

```
 +s   -r
   \ /
-q -*- +q
   / \
 +r   -s
```

